### TC.Agro Analytics Service - HTTP Requests
### NOTE: Make sure the service is running: dotnet run
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5174

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Pending Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/pending
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get Pending Alerts Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/pending/summary?windowHours=24
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get Alert History for a Plot (replace with your PlotId)
# Use the PlotId from your test data in Supabase
@plotId = ae57f8d7-d491-4899-bb39-30124093e683
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/history/{{plotId}}?days=30
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get Alert History with Filters (HighTemperature only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/history/{{plotId}}?days=7&alertType=HighTemperature&status=Pending
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get Alert History with Filters (LowSoilMoisture only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/history/{{plotId}}?days=7&alertType=LowSoilMoisture
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Get Plot Status Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/plots/{{plotId}}/status
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Swagger UI (open in browser)
# Open this URL in your browser: http://localhost:5174/swagger

###
